Dia. 01 Hasty Conclusion from Both
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Probably both, Black and White think that this variation is going to happen. However it is a \cf1\b hasty conclusion\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par White takes at 1 and then Black fills the liberty with 2 and captures the White \'a1\'e2 stones.
\par
\par White shouldn't be satisfied with this result.
\par }
