Dia. 03 Follow up
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If Black plays, he has no chance but to capture with 1.
\par After that White throws-in again with 2 which is the deciding move.
\par
\par Black can't save his stones.
\par Actually the previous variation has \cf1\b already decided the result of the capturing race\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par
\par }
